metadata.name: About Love
metadata.description: This work is a revelation. This is my young self-portrait. I was 19 years old. I was virgin and pure. And these are my deep impressions of kissing and affection. These are my dreams of a man with whom we were never lucky enough to have intimacy) I am infinitely grateful to him for this, because the inexperienced I was able to create Such). And it's very disturbing to talk about it.
